# GoalifyNow WebApp

## Scope

`apps/webapp` — Angular application (standalone components, modern CLI layout).

## Practices

- Prefer standalone components and lazy-loaded routes consistent with existing features
- Use the project's chosen UI and styling approach without introducing parallel design systems
- Keep strings out of templates where the app already uses i18n or shared constants
- Use typed HTTP clients or services matching backend contracts under `backend/GoalifyNow.Api`
- After substantive UI changes, run `pnpm build:web` from the repository root when feasible

## API integration

- Respect environment files under `apps/webapp/src/environments/` for base URLs
- Do not hardcode secrets; use existing configuration mechanisms
